A SCOT has died after a plunging from a hotel balcony in party resort Ibiza.&nbsp;The 26-year-old man is understood to have been found around 11.30pm on Saturday.He was named as Robert Gillespie, from Larbert, in Stirlingshire.Mr Gillespie - who was known as Fraser - was believed to have been staying at a fifth-floor room in the Piscis Park Hotel.An investigation was today under way&nbsp; to determine the cause of death.